  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  birch pollen sensitive subjects

          -  Positive RAST or intracutane skintest

          -  age 18-50

          -  signed informed consent form

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  use of probiotics

          -  known allergy for pets (home setting)

          -  use of medication influencing the immune system

          -  use of antibiotics

          -  lactose intolerance

          -  pregnancy

          -  infection
      </textblock>
